# Next.js web

- Use App Router under `apps/web/`.
- Route groups: public storefront (SEO), seller panel, admin — separate layouts.
- Prefer Server Components for catalog/product pages; client components for interactive cart/auth.
- Call backend via gateway base URL from env (never hardcode production hosts in source).
- Static landing lives in `apps/web/public/` until full app scaffold exists.
